Package gw.cc.exposure.entity

Interface ClaimantSupplier

All Known Implementing Classes:
APDIncident, BaggageIncident, DwellingIncident, FixedPropertyIncident, Incident, InjuryIncident, LivingExpensesIncident, MobilePropertyIncident, OtherStructureIncident, PropertyContentsIncident, PropertyIncident, TripIncident, VehicleIncident
public interface ClaimantSupplier
Interface for objects that know how to provide a claimant and claimant type. This interface is intended to be implemented by Incidents. The implementation of these methods should provide reasonable default values for exposure rules to use to populate the respective fields on automatically created exposures.
